## 1. WHAT KOY IS (the 30-second version)

Koy is a customizable page builder where the same product serves wildly different audiences (traders, tattoo artists, working parents, teens, podcasters, etc.) via persona-tuned templates and blocks. Users get a public URL at `/u/{handle}` that becomes their personal corner of the internet. The vision includes a marketplace where users can buy/sell page layouts (skeleton-only, $8.99 floor, 15% take rate) and a "package" model ($25.99 vertical bundles like Tattoo Package, Hair Stylist Package) that get built reactively based on observed user behavior, not predicted.

**It is NOT:** a productivity tool, a Linktree clone, a calendar app, a Notion competitor. It IS: self-expression with a creator economy underneath.

