## 6. DATA MODEL (current state of production)

### Tables

**profiles** — one per user, auto-created on signup
```
id (uuid, FK to auth.users), handle (unique), display_name, bio,
is_premium (bool), data_sharing (bool), created_at, updated_at
```

**pages** — saved page layouts, multiple per user, only one active
```
id, user_id (FK profiles), name, is_active (bool), page_settings (jsonb),
blocks (jsonb), created_at, updated_at
```
- UNIQUE constraint: only one `is_active=true` per `user_id` (Sprint 1 migration)

**comments** — Discord-style comments on active pages
```
id, page_id (FK pages), author_id (FK profiles), author_name,
author_avatar (default ⭐), message, created_at
```

**user_events** — the "money table" for AI training data licensing
```
id (bigint), user_id (FK profiles, nullable for guests), event_type,
event_data (jsonb), device, shareable (bool default true), created_at
```
- INSERT policy: `auth.uid() = user_id OR user_id IS NULL` (Sprint 1)

**trading_days** — LEGACY, will be dropped in Sprint 3
- Kept for backwards compat during Sprint 2

**calendar_entries** — NEW in Sprint 2, replaces trading_days
```
id, user_id (FK profiles), day, emoji, label, numeric_value, count_value,
journal, mood, color, freeform_blocks (jsonb), created_at, updated_at
unique(user_id, day)
```
- `color` column added in Sprint 2 PR #2 (rainbow calendar capability — per-cell background color override)
- `freeform_blocks` format: `[{type: 'text'|'emoji'|'sticker', content, x: 0-100, y: 0-100, fontSize?, color?}, ...]`
- Coordinates are percentages (cell-size independent)
- Hard cap: 20 elements per cell, client-enforced

**month_archives** — SPECCED, NOT BUILT (Sprint 3)
```
year, month, custom_name, blocks_snapshot (jsonb),
page_settings_snapshot (jsonb), unique(user_id, year, month)
```

### Storage

- `user-uploads` bucket (Sprint 2, requires manual creation)
- Path convention: `{user_id}/{block_id}/{timestamp}-{filename}`
- Limits: 5MB free / 25MB premium, MIME types jpeg/png/webp/gif

